author: rabk295
title: I love the Oldies!
review:
Even though this set isn't very complicated and there isn't much to do with it, I still find this little guy really cool. One of the things I find coolest is th pilot's helmet, which I use for all of my fighter plane pilots.
Not thwe greatest set ever, but I still find it cool.

author: Rgijaba
title: a nice little hover craft.
review: this set is basicly Jet on a little ship with some lights on it and a power saw on the back. i cant imagine what the rock raiders used this for, but i have to give it a 5/5 beacuse there are no real flaws. in a set this small, how could there be?  you should get this if your a rock raiders collector, want Jet for chaep, or want it.
